@hostname = localhost
@port = 32768
@baseUrl = http://{{hostname}}:{{port}}

POST {{baseUrl}}/api/Character
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Name": "Gandalf",
  "Description": "Istar (Mago) e Portador de Narya",
  "Attributes": [
    { "Name": "Inteligência", "Value": "20" },
    { "Name": "Sabedoria", "Value": "19" }
  ],
  "Skills": [
    { "Name": "Arcanismo", "Value": 10 },
    { "Name": "História", "Value": 8 }
  ]
}

### Listar Personagens (GET)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/Character
Accept: application/json

